N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 256.1 - Executive director; certification of papers; notices and reports

State Regulations

The executive director, or such other person as may be
designated by the executive director, is authorized to certify copies of all
papers and documents which are a part of any of the files or records of the
board, to sign and issue all notices or reports of the board. Notes
